{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act22side", "eventName": "照我以火", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "FC-2", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "不幸重逢", "storyInfo": "面對物資不足的問題，維恩和葦草試圖向聚落的居民求助，而塞爾蒙決定打劫商隊。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g6_noblelivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菲舍爾，子爵的緊急信函......", "name": "特別行動隊隊長"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......菲舍爾？", "name": "特別行動隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，你又在思索什麼難題？", "name": "特別行動隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......抱歉。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你對著拼圖走神的時間裡，那個叫阿赫茉妮的菲林可是一刻不停地在行動，就在這座特倫特郡裡。", "name": "特別行動隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請放心，我沒有片刻走神，對她的監視也沒有絲毫鬆懈。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看你的樣子，調查應該沒有什麼進展。", "name": "特別行動隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果這段時間的觀察能夠證明，她依然忠於自己對維多利亞的職責，那麼我會比抓住一個叛徒更高興。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#7$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可從沒看到過你高興的時候。", "name": "特別行動隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我以為上次行動失敗之後，我不會再在這間辦公室見到你了。", "name": "特別行動隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請不要這麼說，行動本身並沒有失敗。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醫院的檢查結果呢？", "name": "特別行動隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "菲舍爾", "content": "急性感染，創口中活性源石碎片較多......"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "菲舍爾", "content": "當然，病情已經被控制住了，請不用擔心。偶發的疼痛並不會影響我的行動。"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，診斷結果我還沒有上報。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#7$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我認為自己尚有能力執行對阿赫茉妮的調查任務，而且，沒有誰會想接手這一地的資訊碎片。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些煙霧彈背後的真實目的，我有責任探清。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......在此期間，我會和所有人保持距離，請放心。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以我處理緊急事態的經驗，還用不著你說這句話。", "name": "特別行動隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要市政廳依然允許你進出，我們特別行動隊就會持續支持你的調查。", "name": "特別行動隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不說聲感謝嗎？", "name": "特別行動隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，算了，我只是想開個玩笑，讓你別一直緊繃著。", "name": "特別行動隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記得抽空看看子爵的信。", "name": "特別行動隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......請柬？", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白了。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g1_victoriavillage", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......聽你的？你要把我們帶到哪裡去？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們不能再這麼往荒野裡面走了，你指的方向根本沒有聚落。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那種寸草不生的地方，別說獵野獸，就連野莓都撿不到。再說，你也不知道哪場雨會帶著小石頭一起砸下來，天災信使都不會從那裡走！", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道穿過那片沼澤要花幾天，口糧的事，找維多利亞人的商隊去搶就是了。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，那個醫生帶的藥也夠。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#8$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不是醫生......她也是要去鎮上的，我們說好了她送我們到鎮上就走。你把她當什麼了？我們的藥箱子？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#7$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就為了你那點私心，所有人都得把自己的東西、自己的命全搭給你，是不是？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#3$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閉嘴，維恩！你要是有意見，怎麼不自己走？你有那個本事嗎？", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#3$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "膽小鬼是活不下去的。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞爾蒙！", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，“葦草”。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我真不喜歡你這個綽號，就跟什麼石頭泥巴似的，遍地都是，也不知道是在叫你還是叫路邊的草，哈哈。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽到你們在吵架。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是這樣......我得跟你說件事。我們去不了圖拉鎮了。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛廣播裡說，軍隊懷疑那邊有兩家工廠在偷偷給深池生產物資，趕走了一批人，爆發了一些衝突。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們現在繼續往那個方向走，別說搭上運載車了，大概剛接近鎮子就會被抓。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......唉，難得又多了一個有本事的人幫忙，好不容易才逃到這裡。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#2$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，說得好像扒上了一輛運載車，你的好日子就來了似的。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#7$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從一家工廠，溜到另一處礦場，直到有一天撞大運，有一輛車把你們帶到塔拉以外的地方......你覺得這很容易？", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#7$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道許多人都是這麼逃的呀。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你只是看到他們走掉了，因為村子被燒、附近找不到能種活莊稼的荒地，所以走掉了。可你又不知道他們最終去了哪裡，是死是活。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說，塔拉在哪裡，走到哪才算是逃出去了，你又知道嗎？地圖上都沒標注過。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別拿這種大問題來嚇唬我！就算我答不上來，難道你就對了？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#7$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......算了算了，我去找這裡的老熟人商量一下，借點乾糧。唉，好像你那麼多話，能把我們十幾個人明天的口糧變出來似的。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "300,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他......很傷心。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然啦，他不喜歡說假話嘛。但找人借東西的時候難免要撒個謊，說自己還會回來，能還上債之類的。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我去幫他。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說話太像那些外地來的維多利亞軍官了，他們不會信任你的。還是說，你很擅長說謊？", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#9$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是，不喜歡打劫他人的做法。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，你的私心......我也不喜歡。它才是那個最大的謊言。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g1_victoriavillage", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你朋友確實說是在這附近見到的深池？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_175", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不然我們為什麼不敢從這附近經過？商隊之間都已經傳開了，現在所有人都寧可繞個大遠路，也要避開這一帶。", "name": "商隊首領"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_175", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不是你們那麼信誓旦旦地保證不會出事......我們是絕對不會到這裡來的。", "name": "商隊首領"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，但是這都快到你們的目的地了，一路上還是什麼也沒看見呀。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_175", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，那都是好些天之前的事情了，也有可能他們已經走遠了。", "name": "商隊首領"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_175", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說當時深池就在急匆匆地趕路，所以都沒正眼瞧我朋友的商隊。", "name": "商隊首領"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊。他當時見到多少人？往哪個方向去了？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_175", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那邊。朝著沒人的荒野走了。具體有多少人，他說數不清，也不敢仔細數。", "name": "商隊首領"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_175", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有必要騙你們，兩位女士。除了深池的那些拿著武器的混蛋，一般的塔拉流氓我們是一點也不用怕的。", "name": "商隊首領"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_175", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "窮地方嘛，流竄的強盜什麼的總是比較多，我們當然也會準備一些安保措施。", "name": "商隊首領"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_175", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時知道橡林郡要長距離移動，我們商隊的路線要改到經過這一帶的時候，我就已經花大價錢給我的人準備武器和防具啦。", "name": "商隊首領"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等一下，陳陳......你看那邊。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡有個......打扮很像深池的人。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snowconutryinside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，最近剛頒佈的新稅收法令確實太苛刻了，要是放在往年，大多數人不至於這麼為難。", "name": "小有積蓄的農場主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我真希望能幫上你們，維恩，還有這位外地來的女士......只是說起來不怕你笑話，我現在的日子也很拮据。", "name": "小有積蓄的農場主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一方面，你要給十幾個人討一頓飯，這要得可不少。另一方面，他們既然人數眾多，有手有腳，也有力氣，還是應該自己想想辦法吧。", "name": "小有積蓄的農場主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也知道，熄火鐘在石高原野上響了好幾年了，可不就是攔著餓肚子的人，不許我們去偷獵貴族們的獵物？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "得了，真的到了要餓死的時候，誰還在乎那些規矩？現在就指望著別人救濟，我看是天生好吃懶做！", "name": "小有積蓄的農場主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不不不，怎麼會呢......他們可都是守規矩的人，我才替他們開口借點吃的呀......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——或者，你們有東西拿來抵押也行。", "name": "小有積蓄的農場主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，維恩，口頭的保證現在不管用啦。", "name": "小有積蓄的農場主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$book_close"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......書？這也不行，女士，這東西用來墊床腳都嫌爛得快。", "name": "小有積蓄的農場主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"focus": "none"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您好，請問有人在嗎？", "name": "疲倦的女聲"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是——", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別答應。", "name": "小有積蓄的農場主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那病女人又帶著人來乞討啦，真煩人。你要是給她開了門，她得靠在門框上跟你說一個鐘頭。", "name": "小有積蓄的農場主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "靠在門框上！她可是感染者啊！我都怕我家的門框上也長出石頭來！", "name": "小有積蓄的農場主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，那幾個討飯的，我還以為去年冬天就該死得差不多了......得了病是很可憐，但誰叫他們四處亂跑招人討厭呀。", "name": "小有積蓄的農場主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，那個聲音......不，不會吧？但我不會聽錯的呀......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維恩，你認識她？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我不知道......唉，還是不要從窗戶縫裡張望了......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_armycrowd", "loop": "true", "channel": "b", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "b", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......打鬥的聲音。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人在驅趕那些感染者嗎？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是，是村子外面，公路上傳來的聲音。", "name": "小有積蓄的農場主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，看看我說什麼......餓肚子的人就是會拿起鋤頭跟人打架的啊！", "name": "小有積蓄的農場主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g1_victoriavillage", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tense_intro", "key": "$tense_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_242", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_243", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別等了，再磨蹭一會，商隊就要過去了。", "name": "暴躁的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我敢打賭維恩這次也討不到吃的。他這樣到處求人，也不嫌丟人。", "name": "暴躁的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些維多利亞人天天對我們擺臉色，我們搶他們一次東西怎麼了？我們不是要加入深池去跟維多利亞人打仗的嗎？", "name": "暴躁的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_243", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，看到我們做這種事，葦草恐怕會生氣吧。", "name": "緊張的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "管她幹嘛。我們不趁著還有力氣跟人打架的時候去搶，難道要等到餓得頭暈眼花了再去？", "name": "暴躁的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且這麼多天了，我們還是頭一次見到商隊，誰知道下一次機會什麼時候才來？", "name": "暴躁的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_243", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那，要不說服葦草跟我們一起動手？那樣至少成功的機率大一點。", "name": "緊張的塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......夠了，別提她了。我們要做的事，跟她有什麼關係。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道你就一直指望著她一個外來人幫我們？", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走，動手。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#10$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_unsheathe"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_attack_ready", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}